snippet.title: Campaign for Common Sense Regulation
snippet.description: The U.S. Senate recently passed the Economic Growth, Regulatory Relief, and Consumer Protection Act. This bill will provide regulatory relief to Main Street financial institutions including credit unions and community banks while maintaining regulations for Wall Street. Tell your U.S. Representative to support S. 2155!
